msgid "KeepSecret"
msgstr "KeepSecret"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.keepsecret.metainfo.xml:9
msgid "Manage passwords"
msgstr "Gere  contrasignos"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.keepsecret.metainfo.xml:16
msgid ""
"Password manager for viewing, editing, creating, or deleting passwords, "
"suitable for both desktop and mobile platforms."
msgstr ""
"Gerente de Contrasignoper vider, modficar, crear o deler contrasignos, "
"convenibile per ambe platteformas de Scriptorio e Mobile"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.keepsecret.metainfo.xml:17
msgid ""
"Works with KeepassXC, KWallet, Gnome Keyring, oo7, and any other password "
"backend that's compatible with the Secret Service system."
msgstr ""
"Functiona con KeepassXC, KWallet, Gnome Keyring, oo7, e ulle altere retro "
"administration de contrasigno que escompatibilecon le systema Secret Service."
